^*Bhondo717:^*N Now, let us discuss the auction.  moe has an in-between hand.  In sayc, he is a bit weak for 2@H and a bit strong for 2@S.  With such a good heart suit, good distribution (the singleton diamond), and spade support, I like his choice of bidding 2@H. However, once kia bids 3@H, moe should bid 3@S, to allow kia to bid 4 spades with the appropriate hand.  And, it turns out 4 spades or 4 hearts makes, with different play.  Over 3@S, kia should pass, because although he has a good hand, his club points and diamond points may be wasted. Thus, I think 3@H or 3@S is the right level.|
