^*Bhondo717:^*N So, in a live auction where the opponents bid strongly and have not yet established a fit, it is best to be more cautious, unless you have a very good suit. The reason you worry when they have not found a fit, is the following:
As I have said previously, if they have a fit, then you likely have a fit as well. If they have a fit, we are short in that suit, making it more likely that we have length in another suit. However, the converse is also true.  If they do not have a fit, then we probably do not have a fit either.|
